+## Customization Options
+
+In `app.py` (lines 37-40), you can customize the banner appearance:
+
+### 1. Banner Zoom Level
+```python
+BANNER_ZOOM = "100%"  # Adjust the zoom level
+```
+- `"100%"` = Normal size (default)
+- `"120%"` = Zoom in (shows less of the image, more detailed)
+- `"80%"` = Zoom out (shows more of the image)
+- `"cover"` = Cover entire container (original behavior)
+- `"contain"` = Fit entire image within container
+
+### 2. Banner Position
+```python
+BANNER_POSITION = "center"  # Adjust which part of the image is visible
+```
+- `"center"` = Center the image (default)
+- `"top"` = Show top portion of image
+- `"bottom"` = Show bottom portion of image
+- `"left"` = Show left portion of image
+- `"right"` = Show right portion of image
+- `"center top"` = Center horizontally, show top
+- `"center bottom"` = Center horizontally, show bottom
+- `"25% 75%"` = Custom positioning (X% Y%)
+
+### 3. Title Color
+```python
+TITLE_COLOR = "#FFD700"  # Color for "Mai Shen Yun" title
+```
+Common colors:
+- `"#FFD700"` = Gold (default)
+- `"white"` = White
+- `"#FF6B6B"` = Red
+- `"#4ECDC4"` = Turquoise
+- `"#95E1D3"` = Mint
+- Any valid CSS color (hex, rgb, color name)
